N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7309.4 - Medical diets

State Regulations

The director shall require that any medical diet, prescribed for a youth by a physician, dentist, or other authorized facility
health services staff member, is provided to such youth. Notes
